data.description: As stunning and elegant as a model home with palatial upgrades.  Beautiful laminate and tile flooring throughout, plantation shutters T/O, remodeled kitchen with 4X6 walk in pantry. State of the art appliances, 3 bed, 2 1/2 bath, 2 family rooms- includes a huge 2nd floor family room. Every room is large and spacious, elegant & palatial light fixtures, ceiling fans and bath fixtures. 3 car garage W/ finished interior. Beautifully landscaped front and rear plus cobblestone steps and lighting. Even more beautiful at night than it is during the day. 2 patios, one with an out door movie screen, corner lot with mountain view, no housing behind and only one house to the side.  Cool off in the pristine, above ground pool in a time when having a pool is a pot of gold.  Edison string lighting enhances the outdoor experience. Photos tell the whole story and the story is one you will want to call yours. Enjoy the open, blue sky filled location with shopping and services just 5 minutes away.
